15	Amlodipine	calcium channel blocker,antihypertensive,angina,vasodilator	Amlodipine is a long-acting calcium channel blocker used to treat hypertension and coronary artery disease including chronic stable angina and vasospastic angina. It works by relaxing blood vessels.
